	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Cape Island</placeName> <date>1st July</date>.</p>
				<p>My dear <addressee>Mr Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">I write this to say &#8220;how<lb/> do you do&#44;&#8221; &#38; &#8220;good bye&#8221; I was quite<lb/> sorry I did not see you before our<lb/> departure. How did you enjoy<lb/> yourself &#63; Did you see many friends&#63;<lb/> When you write tell me all about<lb/> your visit &#40;I have forgotten the place<lb/> that you went to was it <placeName>Baltimore</placeName><lb/> or <placeName>Salem</placeName>&#41; The only news that I can<lb/> write about will concern all of our<lb/> family for I <hi rend="underline">flatter</hi> myself that<lb/> you would be more interested in<lb/> our affairs that in strangers.<lb/> The weather has been delightful<lb/> so cool we bathe every day<lb/> expect the bathing will be a great<lb/> deal better next week on account<lb/> of the tide being higher  &#40;the tide is<lb/> regulated by the moon&#41;</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>The other morning <persName>Selina</persName> &#38; myself<lb/> were bathing were were not looking<lb/> at the breakers &#38; before we could<lb/> do anything down we went flat.<lb/> I was dreadfully frightened I<lb/> tried to <sic>calck</sic><add>&#63;</add> me but could<lb/> not at last a swell came &#38;<lb/> that brought me to the top<lb/> I swallowed a pint of<lb/> salt water. All my friends<lb/> tell me they think I am look<lb/>ing a great deal better when I<lb/> was here a day or two I weighed 86 &#38; this morning I weighed<lb/> 88&#8212;you can judge for your<lb/>self when we meet which I<lb/> hope will be soon you better<lb/> think of coming down it would<lb/> be a great benefit to you to<lb/> smell some fresh pure<lb/> salt air. I must now bid you<lb/> good bye as ma wants to write</p>
			<pb n="3"/>
				<p>Ma &#38; <persName>Selina</persName> send their love to you<lb/> hoping to see you soon.</p>
			<p rend="indent(7)">I remain your fond</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)"><persName role="author">Corinna</persName></p>
				<p>P. S. Kiss <persName>Dew Drop</persName> for me tell<lb/> her to <hi rend="underline">write me</hi> a letter.</p>
		</body>
